gw.api.profiler

Class QuerySummary

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.profiler.QuerySummary

  • public class QuerySummary
extends java.lang.Object
    Encapsulates the execution of a single SQL query contained in a ProfilerFrame whose tag is ProfilerTag.EXECUTE_QUERY_TAG. At a minimum, this includes the query string, the query arguments, and the elapsed time required to execute the query. If stacktrace analysis is enabled during profiling, this object will also contain the full stacktrace of the query, a "filtered" stack trace of the query (which elides elements that are typically uninteresting), and the PCF stack trace of the query.
    Author:
    cgross
